      "raw_text": "WASHINGTON. Dec. 3.--The meet\ning of the Women's club and others\nopposed to the seating of Senator\nReed Smoot took place this morning\nin the Church of the Covenant. Reso-\nbuttons of protest were adopted for\ntransmission to the senate. Among\nthose making addresses were DR..\nSarah Elliott of the Woman's coun-\nell, former resident of Salt Lake, now\nliving at Philadelphia, and Mrs.\nCharles owen of the Utah American"
